{
  "uid": "v12-0-scenes-vars",
  "title": "Grafana 12.0 \u2014 Scenes Chained Variables",
  "description": "Scenes is the mandatory dashboard runtime as of 12.0. This demo shows Scenes' chained-variable evaluation \u2014 `$job` drives `$instance` drives the panel queries, all re-rendering reactively.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "v12.0",
    "scenes",
    "variables",
    "v12-demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-15m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_prom",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prom"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "job",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "Job",
        "datasource": {
          "uid": "${ds_prom}",
          "type": "prometheus"
        },
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(up, job)",
          "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "multi": false,
        "current": {
          "text": "grafana",
          "value": "grafana"
        },
        "hide": 0
      },
      {
        "name": "instance",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "Instance (chained on $job)",
        "datasource": {
          "uid": "${ds_prom}",
          "type": "prometheus"
        },
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(up{job=\"$job\"}, instance)",
          "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "multi": false,
        "hide": 0
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10000,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "tags": [
        "demo-guide"
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1.2rem;background:#1a2a3a;border-left:4px solid #5794f2;border-radius:6px;font-family:system-ui\"><div style=\"font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.18em;color:#8aa9d0;margin-bottom:.3rem\">DEMO GUIDE</div><div style=\"font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.6rem\">Grafana 12.0 \u2014 Scenes Chained Variables</div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem\"><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#5794f2;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83c\udfaf What you're looking at</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Grafana 12 runs every dashboard on the Scenes runtime. Variables form a reactive graph: when $job changes, $instance re-evaluates, then the panels re-query. Only the panels whose inputs actually changed re-run.</div></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#73bf69;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83e\uddea Try this</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Switch the Job dropdown \u2014 Instance auto-populates. Pick an instance \u2014 every panel re-queries.</div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:.8rem;padding-top:.6rem;border-top:1px solid #2d3e54;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udcda <strong style=\"color:#fff\">Learn more</strong>: <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/dashboards/variables/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Grafana docs</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/whatsnew/whats-new-in-v12-0/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">v12 What's New</a></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Scenes runtime (12.0)\n\nSwitch **Job** at the top \u2014 **Instance** re-populates automatically because Scenes re-evaluates every variable whose query references `$job`. Panel queries re-run only when their inputs change.\n\nThis is the declarative dataflow that `dashboardScene=true` enables. The flag is effectively mandatory in 12 and locked on in 13."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "up for `$job / $instance`",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "up{job=\"$job\", instance=\"$instance\"}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "DOWN",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "UP",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "up for `$job / $instance`. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/dashboards/variables/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "scrape_duration_seconds \u2014 `$job`",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "scrape_duration_seconds{job=\"$job\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 4,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "last"
          ],
          "placement": "right"
        }
      },
      "description": "scrape_duration_seconds \u2014 `$job`. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/dashboards/variables/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "scrape_samples_scraped \u2014 `$job / $instance`",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 18
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "scrape_samples_scraped{job=\"$job\", instance=\"$instance\"}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 20
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": false
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single"
        }
      },
      "description": "scrape_samples_scraped \u2014 `$job / $instance`. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/dashboards/variables/"
    }
  ]
}